{"tid":2433023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19名緬甸警員流亡海外 表示無法服從打壓人民指令","createTime":"2021-03-04T16:40:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T15:34:37.000Z","uid":125168,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"35a927ba854e316fe439aba8d70d0d5e8661e8d4","tid":2433023,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:40:09.000Z","msg":"印度東北部的米佐拉姆（Mizoram）警方今天證實，19名緬甸警察因為拒絕執行軍方命令，昨午變節越過北凡萊拜鎮的邊境尋求態護，地方政府正評估他們的健康狀況，並為他們作安排。印度當局說：「他們說，他們接到軍政府下達的指令，他們實在無法服從那些指令，所以決定逃亡。」<br />\n<br />\n社交媒體近日已多次有帖文指有警員響應公民抗命、反對軍事政變，部份甚至被拘捕，但今次是首次有報道指警員流亡國外。印度和緬甸共享1,643公里長的陸地邊界，亦是成千上萬緬甸難民的家園，包括羅興亞人和少數民族欽族人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210304/OMZCVJ52FJD6JOYJ6XF7TKEMTY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3UySG9tUf3omEjSUTdczENN5eHZjhsMQY9ouAjvz42U4-mZWlxEiYAR08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210304%2FOMZCVJ52FJD6JOYJ6XF7TKEMTY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3UySG9tUf3omEjSUTdczENN5eHZjhsMQY9ouAjvz42U4-mZWlxEiYAR08&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUr2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=884b000d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210304%2FOMZCVJ52FJD6JOYJ6XF7TKEMTY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3UySG9tUf3omEjSUTdczENN5eHZjhsMQY9ouAjvz42U4-mZWlxEiYAR08&h=fbaaa2ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210304/OMZCVJ52FJD6JOYJ6XF7TKEMTY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3UySG9tUf3omEjSUTdczENN5eHZjhsMQY9ouAjvz42U4-mZWlxEiYAR08</a>"},{"pid":"dec26c46199211eef1a9a913f8d0dbbace51d02c","tid":2433023,"ui